# Views

Read [docs/FRONTEND.md](../../docs/FRONTEND.md), [docs/I18N.md](../../docs/I18N.md).

- ERB + Tailwind CSS 4; copy the nearest existing component.
- Components: `app/views/<feature>/components/_*.html.erb` — one partial per list item; extract ~10 repeating lines.
- Files under 150 lines.
- User-facing copy: I18n keys, not hardcoded strings on touched lines.
- No view specs unless policy changes.
